  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765121378\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765121378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765121378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/32ed0e8802c146de2e0efa1da4463da5.avif?t=1765121378\" width=610 height=246 /></span><br><br>Rotatex 2 is an independent story with new adventures.  <br>You have to rotate the level and solve puzzles.  <br><br>Feature of game:  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure with the rotation of the level <br></li><li>Convenient control <br></li><li>Challenging levels <br></li><li>Physics, doors, keys and traps. </li></ul> <br>In the game you have to smoothly rotate the level and jump over obstacles.  <br>A cat named Rotatex is able to cling to walls and use sharp spikes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b3aad6e8abe34b25eb194ddce6355b4a.poster.avif?t=1765121378\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b3aad6e8abe34b25eb194ddce6355b4a.webm?t=1765121378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b3aad6e8abe34b25eb194ddce6355b4a.mp4?t=1765121378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/32ed0e8802c146de2e0efa1da4463da5.avif?t=1765121378\" width=610 height=246 /></span><br><br>Rotatex 2 is an independent story with new adventures.  <br>You have to rotate the level and solve puzzles.  <br><br>Feature of game:  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure with the rotation of the level <br></li><li>Convenient control <br></li><li>Challenging levels <br></li><li>Physics, doors, keys and traps. </li></ul> <br>In the game you have to smoothly rotate the level and jump over obstacles.  <br>A cat named Rotatex is able to cling to walls and use sharp spikes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b3aad6e8abe34b25eb194ddce6355b4a.poster.avif?t=1765121378\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b3aad6e8abe34b25eb194ddce6355b4a.webm?t=1765121378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1474860/extras/b3aad6e8abe34b25eb194ddce6355b4a.mp4?t=1765121378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
